Insider Activity


Individual




Stephen James Luczo



Mr. Stephen J. Luczo is Chairman & Chief Executive Officer at Seagate Technology LLC and Chairman & Chief Executive Officer at Seagate Technology Plc. He is on the Board of Directors at World Wildlife Fund, Inc. Mr. Luczo was previously employed as an Independent Director by Microsoft Corp., Chief Executive Officer by Seagate Technology, Inc. /Old/, and Senior Managing Director-Global Technology Group by Bear, Stearns & Co., Inc. He also served on the board at Xiotech Corp. and Crystal Decisions, Inc. He received his undergraduate degree from Stanford University and an MBA from Stanford Graduate School of Business.



