Mr. Stephen J. LuczoSeagate Technology LLCCupertino, CAJoined Seagate in 1993 as SVP of corporate development and following a series of promotions became president and COO, CEO, and chairman. In 2004 he resigned as CEO, but retained his position as chairman. After working as a private investor from 2006-2009, he rejoined Seagate as president and CEO.2012 Third QuarterAdded to: Microsoft Corp. - Redmond, WAMicrosoft develops, licenses, and supports software products. Revenues are $86 billion.















 















 











